OL,3,CMurder investigation underway as
OL,4,Ctributes made to 'loving dad'
OL,6,FFamily members have paid tribute to a
OL,7,F'loving dad' who was found dead at his
OL,8,FWrexham home on Sunday 23 February.
OL,10,FCraig Richardson, 37, was pronounced
OL,11,Fdeceased when officers were called to
OL,12,Fan address on the Gwynant estate in
OL,13,FAcrefair, Wrexham.
OL,15,FNorth Wales Police has confirmed that
OL,16,FThomas Iveson, 30, of the Plas Madoc
OL,17,Farea, has been charged with murder.
