OL,6,FHe was remanded in custody before
OL,7,Fappearing at Mold Magistrates' Court
OL,8,Fthis morning (Thursday, 27th
OL,9,FFebruary), where he was further
OL,10,Fremanded into custody to appear before
OL,11,FMold Crown Court tomorrow (Friday,
OL,12,F28th February).
OL,14,FA second man, a 32-year-old from
OL,15,FWrexham, who was arrested in
OL,16,Fconnection with the incident remains
OL,17,Fon bail as the investigation continues.
OL,19,FIn a tribute, the victim's family
OL,20,Fdescribed him as "full of fun" and say
OL,21,Fhe will be "missed forever".
