OL,6,FThe tribute read: "Craig was a loving
OL,7,Fson, dad, brother, uncle, nephew,
OL,8,Fcousin, partner and a friend to many
OL,9,Fwho we all loved with all of our
OL,10,Fhearts.
OL,12,F"Everybody who really knew Craig will
OL,13,Fsay he had the biggest heart, would
OL,14,Fgive you his last and was full of fun.
OL,15,FCraig will be missed forever, and in
OL,16,Four hearts forever and ever".
